Had the same issue. Seems like in the aggregations the fieldName should be the actual metric_name specified in the "metric" : <metric name> field for topN query.
"aggregations": [
    { "type": "longMax", "name": "max_purchase_amount", "fieldName": "purchase_amount" }
  ],

Should be : 

"aggregations": [
    { "type": "longMax", "name": "purchase_amount", "fieldName": "purchase_amount" }
  ],

